[gd_scene load_steps=36 format=3]

; WATER — Open lagoon with swimmable pool.
; Landmarks: Sunken Shipwreck (tilted hull + broken mast), Pillar Island
;   (tall single column with star on top), Deep Trench, Sand Bar Beach,
;   Coral Shelf.
; Tiers: trench floor / lagoon surface / sand bar / pillar summit.
; 10 enemies (piranha plants on beaches, goombas on sand bars, bobombs),
;   35 coins, pillar star, vanish cap inside hull.

